Inspired by fluffytree-threejs (https://github.com/mreinstein/fluffytree-threejs)
Original Copyright (c) Michael Reinstein — MIT License

This is a self-contained re-implementation of the same idea (low-poly stylized
"fluffy" trees built from a tapered trunk + clusters of overlapping crown puffs)
adapted for Tethical's Three.js pipeline, with biome-aware presets and merged
geometry output suitable for instanced rendering.

